{"tid":1919332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(警世少長文) 轉載自立場：網絡吸精瓶 — 吸掉人民憤怒的「三萬 thx」","createTime":"2020-03-10T17:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T14:44:21.000Z","uid":76365,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc6c5c04e3046834124c2cc96a4ade659d0f722","tid":1919332,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"反送中中期，我 unlike 了「作者」的 page，但此前他有件事説得挺對的：網絡會吸掉人的憤怒。就像《GTA》面市，槍殺案反而少了。<br />\n<br />\n網絡情緒，是現實情緒的弱化投射。我小學年代，在一間教堂課後託管，有欺凌別人，亦有被別人欺凌，往來中塑造了今天的我。那時我聽見社會討論「網絡欺凌」，O 哂嘴，如同聽見「電子拜山」&mdash; 面對面的怒鬥才是大勇，放上網絡，發送當發怒，有什麼好怕的？<br />\n<br />\n一般香港八、九十後，網齡都很高，「認真就輸了」漸成了一種調節機制。當網絡為現實帶來不必要負荷，後者自會用最省力的方式處理前者。之前譚家博（蒸魚安）來青年文學獎乞奬找碴，我們莊員留言字面看似憤怒，實情鍵盤後大家都在笑騎騎，傳閱他很樣衰的自拍。<br />\n<br />\n所以真的不難想像，警察專頁 admin 處於什麼狀態：黑警不是 KOL、不是商業公司，是沒有動機認真經營網絡的。黑警只是數位（digital）清道夫 &mdash; 人們對各式警暴的憤怒再大，吸進了網絡，成了嬲嬲，就是數位垃圾。「3 萬 thx」是最典型的數位垃圾：線下殺警的大欲，成了線上套語，刷了一波 status、comment、短片，就什麼都留不低。你們想殺害的目標，拿「30 萬 thx」來整圖，是在嘲諷：你們自吹自擂的憤怒，最後居然合成出這麼人畜無害的形狀，真無能啊。而你們回應的方法，卻是製造更多數位垃圾，猶不覺半分受辱。<br />\n<br />\n後半段：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%90%B8%E7%B2%BE%E7%93%B6-%E5%90%B8%E6%8E%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92%E7%9A%84-%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC-thx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%2593%25B6-%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%258E%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2586%25A4%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%259A%2584-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2590%25AC-thx%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=958c96df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%2593%25B6-%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%258E%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2586%25A4%25E6%2580%2592%25E7%259A%2584-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2590%25AC-thx%2F&h=d92bb4cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%90%B8%E7%B2%BE%E7%93%B6-%E5%90%B8%E6%8E%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92%E7%9A%84-%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC-thx/</a><br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\nAction speaks louder than words. 我地要做多D"},{"pid":"fbf53973fd70d6b53cf0a575c98e283914d47b69","tid":1919332,"uid":76365,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"入link幫立場賺click rate, thx"},{"pid":"ba4a75fe66d1ab05705d77d541b70705beb49a2c","tid":1919332,"uid":76365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"你們能稍稍察覺一下，這場抗爭 clich&eacute; 串流盛宴到底有多白痴嗎？"},{"pid":"8572294e0c10572e771e4501f51b20bdaa9968ba","tid":1919332,"uid":76365,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"憤怒的話，看書也好、健身也好、賺錢也好，至少你有更多才學、體能、財力，去支撐你未來的大爆發。"},{"pid":"c3e14cbf529224db192ac71cdee5ab229530bbd4","tid":1919332,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660c99a532b2b23de30c0a6fe13a288129571b0a","tid":1919332,"uid":101051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"抱歉！你找的網頁已不存在或輸入錯誤的網址。"},{"pid":"2ed8280662e777c403fbe46680e72dcda13391d1","tid":1919332,"uid":76365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"訓唔著？睇書啦<br />\n《香港民族論》<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/749052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/749052</a>"},{"pid":"0230849934b9e8f43d5f1a61956fccb4edcb6f8e","tid":1919332,"uid":59297,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"一早睇到呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係好難改呢個問題，始終做實事嘅係少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"